WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.166 --> 00:00:02.100
Are you all right?

2
00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:05.133
I'm fine, you're bleeding, and you told me it's fine

3
00:00:05.133 --> 00:00:06.700
I promised you the language to say him 1,200.

4
00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:08.000
You shouldn't have seen you again

5
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:08.900
My bleeding is my business

6
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:10.300
It has nothing to do with you if I die

7
00:00:11.066 --> 00:00:12.866
Hey, I broke my promise.

8
00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:16.000
You promised you would never see me again

9
00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:17.800
But I didn't promise him not to meet you.

10
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:19.666
Why is this person so unreasonable?

11
00:00:19.666 --> 00:00:21.200
I took the initiative, I forced you

12
00:00:21.200 --> 00:00:23.700
You'd better lie still in my arms

13
00:00:23.766 --> 00:00:26.200
The wound is bleeding, it's you who is uncomfortable

14
00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:28.500
Can you stop being so gentle with me?

15
00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.300
Even if you hate me

16
00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:32.100
Also wait for your wound to heal

17
00:00:32.666 --> 00:00:34.100
Don't mess with me here now

18
00:00:34.300 --> 00:00:35.800
I'm really worried about you.

